[[File:Gardener (unused) chathead.png|left]]
'''Gardeners''' were unreleased members of the [[Group of Advanced Gardeners]] that were added to the game files with the release of Farming. It is unknown where they were intended to appear, but presumably they would have protected players' [[Spirit Tree Patch]]es; however, this feature was removed before launch. When it was re-added in an update in 2006, [[Frizzy Skernip]], [[Praistan Ebola]], and [[Yulf Squecks]] were added to watch over Spirit Tree Patches instead, and the gardeners were removed from the game. As a result, they have never been present in ''Old School RuneScape''.
